net.floodlightcontroller.util

类 InstructionUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.floodlightcontroller.util.InstructionUtils

  • public class InstructionUtils
extends java.lang.Object
    Convert OFInstructions to and from dpctl/ofctl-style strings. Used primarily by the static flow pusher to store and retreive flow entries.

      • statTriggerToJsonString

        public static void statTriggerToJsonString(com.fasterxml.jackson.core.JsonGenerator jsonGen,
                                           org.projectfloodlight.openflow.protocol.instruction.OFInstructionStatTrigger s)
        Append OFInstructionStatsTrigger object to an existing JsonGenerator. This method assumes the field name of the instruction has been written already, if required. The appended data will be formatted as follows: { "flags":[ f1, f2, f3, ..., fn ], "thresholds":[ { "oxs_type":"l", "value":"v" }, { "oxs_type":"m", "value":"v" }, ..., { "oxs_type":"n", "value":"v" } ] }
        参数:
        jsonGen -
        s -

      • statTriggerToJsonString

        public static java.lang.String statTriggerToJsonString(org.projectfloodlight.openflow.protocol.instruction.OFInstructionStatTrigger s)
        Create OFInstructionStatsTrigger JSON object string. This method assumes the field name of the instruction will be written externally, if required. The appended JSON string will be formatted as follows: { "flags":[ f1, f2, f3, ..., fn ], "thresholds":[ { "oxs_type":"l", "value":"v" }, { "oxs_type":"m", "value":"v" }, ..., { "oxs_type":"n", "value":"v" } ] }
        参数:
        s -
